sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant OP as Tenant/Admin
    participant API as Control-plane API
    participant WK as Worker (apply + NextHopResolver)
    participant DS as dpstat (privileged C)
    participant BE as Backend / OUT segment
    participant NH as nexthop_map (BPF)
    participant XDP as XDP hot path

    Note over OP,XDP: Declare + immediate resolve
    OP->>API: create/enable service (single IPv4 /32)
    API->>API: validate single-host dest (reject CIDR)
    API-->>WK: enqueue SERVICE_UPDATE apply job
    WK->>WK: apply config, mark_active
    WK->>DS: request_resolve(dp_id, service_ip)
    DS->>BE: ARP request (service_ip on OUT)
    BE-->>DS: ARP reply (dst MAC)
    DS->>NH: update dp_id -> {dst_mac, OUT src_mac, resolved=1}

    Note over WK,NH: Periodic refresh (every 30 min)
    WK->>DS: resolve_once() per enabled service + evict others
    DS->>BE: ARP request
    alt reply within bounded retries
        BE-->>DS: ARP reply
        DS->>NH: refresh entry (RCU-atomic)
    else no reply after N retries
        DS->>NH: mark resolved=0 (fail-closed)
    end

    Note over XDP,NH: Hot path per clean frame
    XDP->>NH: lookup nexthop_map[meta.service_id]
    alt resolved
        NH-->>XDP: {dst_mac, src_mac}
        XDP->>XDP: memcpy eth dst/src (TTL intact) + redirect OUT
    else unresolved / missing
        NH-->>XDP: (none)
        XDP->>XDP: record_drop(DR_NEXTHOP_UNRESOLVED) -> XDP_DROP
    end
